ZH: 我们需要在今天之前缴清房租。
EN: We need to pay the rent before today.

ZH: 公司规定每月需要缴交社保。
EN: The company requires us to contribute to social insurance every month.

ZH: 我们可以通过网上银行缴纳水费。
EN: We can pay the water bill online through the bank.

ZH: 请您在周五之前缴交书面报告。
EN: Please submit the written report before Friday.

ZH: 这本书已经过期，请缴还图书馆。
EN: This book is overdue, please return it to the library.

ZH: 他们每个月都要缴纳一定金额的税款。
EN: They have to pay a certain amount of tax every month.

ZH: 学费必须在开学前一周内全部缴清。
EN: Tuition fees must be paid in full one week before the start of classes.

ZH: 我们必须缴纳停车费才能停在这里。
EN: We need to pay the parking fee to park here.

ZH: 请在交门票时缴费用。
EN: Please pay the fee when buying the ticket.

ZH: 他不愿意缴纳额外的费用。
EN: He is not willing to pay the extra fee.

ZH: 这家餐厅只接受现金缴款。
EN: This restaurant only accepts cash payment.

ZH: 从今年开始，我们必须缴纳额外的健康保险费。
EN: Starting from this year, we have to pay additional health insurance fees.

ZH: 我们必须在下个月底前缴交社区维护费。
EN: We must pay the community maintenance fee before the end of next month.

ZH: 请在领取车票时缴付费用。
EN: Please pay the fee when collecting the ticket.

ZH: 她总是按时缴纳房租。
EN: She always pays the rent on time.

ZH: 我已经缴付了押金，可以搬进新公寓了。
EN: I have paid the deposit and can move into the new apartment.

ZH: 请在入场时缴纳门票。
EN: Please pay the entrance fee when entering.

ZH: 我们必须按规定时间缴交使用费。
EN: We must pay the usage fee on time as stipulated.

ZH: 请在前台缴交办公室租金。
EN: Please pay the office rent at the front desk.

ZH: 过了交费期限，将会被罚款。
EN: There will be a fine for late payment after the due date.
